title: Strictly Come Dancing beats The X Factor in the ratings - Brentwoodweeklynews.co.uk
text:
Strictly Come Dancing jived all over The X Factor in the ratings when the two talent shows clashed on Sunday. The BBC ballroom show drew an average audience of 8.09 million with a 33.1 per cent share of the total TV audience.
 Brentwoodweeklynews.co.uk.
